WEBVTT

00:08.480 --> 00:11.240
I just want to break free
from this prison.

00:12.120 --> 00:13.600
I just want to live my life
without going against my will.

00:14.120 --> 00:15.520
Can't I do that?

00:17.160 --> 00:18.680
Do you take me

00:21.240 --> 00:22.600
for a warden?

00:24.480 --> 00:28.400
Can't you see that I protect you
from the wind and rain every day?

00:28.480 --> 00:33.840
Do you think everything will go well
when you do woodcrafting?

00:35.800 --> 00:38.840
You're naive and foolish.

00:40.160 --> 00:43.040
All the land in the world
belongs to the emperor!

00:43.680 --> 00:47.720
Once the fame and fortune are gone,

00:48.240 --> 00:51.120
the real prison awaits you!

01:23.520 --> 01:26.240
Sir, the imperial physician,
Physician Li, has arrived.

01:37.000 --> 01:40.000
Invite him to come in
and examine the young master.

01:40.520 --> 01:41.360
Yes.

01:46.240 --> 01:47.880
Tell the imperial physician to go back.

01:48.520 --> 01:49.600
I won't see him.

01:49.680 --> 01:51.880
The physician said if you don't meet him,

01:51.960 --> 01:53.720
we should show you this.

03:19.040 --> 03:22.480
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL BLOSSOM
BY AUTHOR ZIZI FROM QIDIAN CHINESE WEBSITE

03:26.960 --> 03:29.480
Mr. Chen, I'm bidding farewell
to you today.

03:30.080 --> 03:33.320
If there's any inconvenience caused,
please forgive me.

03:33.400 --> 03:35.160
You're too serious, Mr. Song.

03:35.760 --> 03:40.240
I'm nothing more than a commoner,
but I've been bothering you for some time.

03:40.320 --> 03:42.480
I am sorry.

03:42.560 --> 03:46.080
I don't like your character,

03:46.160 --> 03:48.920
but I know that you're talented.

03:49.800 --> 03:52.720
Why are you willing to
work for a farm girl?

03:58.280 --> 04:01.680
I am a tainted sinner

04:01.760 --> 04:04.320
and I am old now.

04:04.840 --> 04:08.200
But Young Lady Zhao didn't mind it
and took me as her servant.

04:08.720 --> 04:10.840
I'm satisfied to live
the rest of my life in peace.

04:12.440 --> 04:14.760
You're so willing to submit.

04:14.840 --> 04:18.120
That makes me even more
curious about Young Lady Zhao.

04:30.200 --> 04:32.040
Fortunately, your condition
hasn't worsened.

04:34.320 --> 04:37.840
Take two servings each morning
and evening starting from today.

04:39.000 --> 04:40.680
Young master, please take the medicine.

04:40.760 --> 04:42.800
Young Lady Zhao
came here despite the danger.

04:42.880 --> 04:44.560
-Don't let her down.
-Don't talk too much.

04:50.720 --> 04:54.600
I thought I made it clear last time.

04:56.000 --> 04:58.800
Nothing in this world
is more important than your life.

04:59.680 --> 05:01.280
Why are you torturing yourself?

05:02.720 --> 05:06.120
I… I'm not using my illness to coerce you.

05:09.160 --> 05:11.800
It's just that your question

05:12.320 --> 05:14.400
got to the bottom of my heart.

05:15.280 --> 05:18.200
I know how you feel.

05:18.960 --> 05:22.400
But your grandfather transferred you to
be the officer of the Ministry of Rites.

05:22.920 --> 05:23.920
Did he advise you about this?

05:25.960 --> 05:28.200
You can't even take care of yourself.

05:28.720 --> 05:30.960
Why bother thinking
about protecting others?

05:32.600 --> 05:34.520
I have always respected my grandfather.

05:35.400 --> 05:38.880
What he said was never wrong.

05:40.400 --> 05:42.040
But the only thing is marriage.

05:43.200 --> 05:45.320
I can't just judge
whether it's right or not

05:46.200 --> 05:47.720
without considering willingness.

05:51.440 --> 05:53.960
If I were not born into a wealthy family,

05:56.880 --> 05:59.000
if I were a poor and happy carpenter,

06:01.040 --> 06:02.720
would I have more freedom?

06:04.000 --> 06:05.800
There are differences
between men and women,

06:06.680 --> 06:08.560
but in the matter of marriage,

06:09.520 --> 06:11.360
I am almost the same as you.

06:13.240 --> 06:16.400
You compare yourself to this wooden bird.
I understand.

06:18.960 --> 06:20.240
But have you ever thought about this?

06:20.840 --> 06:22.520
People come and go
in the Grand Secretariat.

06:23.520 --> 06:25.040
Mr. Wu mediates people
in the imperial court.

06:25.120 --> 06:26.760
It's physically and mentally exhausting.

06:27.400 --> 06:30.720
Whether you get married or not,
he needs your support.

06:31.760 --> 06:33.120
If you have a successful career

06:33.200 --> 06:34.920
and can help the Wu family
to revitalize the family fortune,

06:35.000 --> 06:37.160
he will never force you to get married.

06:38.240 --> 06:39.640
You can fight for freedom.

06:40.480 --> 06:43.280
This is true no matter
what family you are born into.

06:50.280 --> 06:53.560
I was simple-minded
and on a wild goose chase.

06:55.040 --> 06:58.640
To keep defying my grandfather
will only hurt us both.

07:00.680 --> 07:04.480
If His Majesty recognizes me
and it revitalizes the Wu family,

07:05.440 --> 07:08.320
I will have the right
to choose for myself.

07:10.320 --> 07:11.960
Man is not a tool made of wood and stone.

07:12.040 --> 07:15.120
Even if you're trapped,
you should take good care of yourself.

07:15.640 --> 07:17.520
Only then will you
have the strength to fight.

07:28.240 --> 07:29.640
The rain has stopped.

07:31.120 --> 07:32.160
I should go now.

07:47.320 --> 07:48.640
Mr. Song.

07:48.720 --> 07:50.800
Young Lady Zhao
sent me to pick up Mr. Chen.

07:54.680 --> 07:55.640
Didn't she come?

07:56.160 --> 07:57.520
Did something happen?

07:57.600 --> 07:59.320
I'm just following her order.

07:59.400 --> 08:01.920
I don't know anything else.
Please forgive me.

08:03.040 --> 08:07.600
Mr. Song has prepared gifts for her,
but she only sent her servant over.

08:08.200 --> 08:10.440
She's such a proud person.

08:13.000 --> 08:13.840
Lu Ming.

08:14.720 --> 08:17.080
Send someone to bring the gifts
to Young Lady Zhao.

08:17.160 --> 08:18.080
Yes.

08:18.160 --> 08:19.000
-Goodbye.
-Goodbye.

08:19.080 --> 08:20.040
Wait a minute!

08:27.480 --> 08:28.360
Physician Li?

08:30.640 --> 08:32.480
Young Lady Zhao
pretended to be Physician Li.

08:32.559 --> 08:33.640
I caught Su Lan.

08:33.720 --> 08:35.360
She's in the carriage.

08:42.960 --> 08:46.520
IMPERIAL BULLETIN: CORRUPTION IN DENGZHOU
PEOPLE SUFFER FAMINE AND GREAT MISERY

08:52.960 --> 08:54.560
Thank you for
your hard work, Physician Li.

08:54.640 --> 08:55.520
Please go and rest.

08:56.120 --> 08:58.640
Thank you so much, Mr. Song.

09:03.320 --> 09:05.240
-Lu Ming.
-Yes.

09:05.840 --> 09:08.600
Go and invite Young Lady Zhao.

09:08.680 --> 09:09.600
Yes.

09:15.600 --> 09:16.640
Young Lady Zhao.

09:18.600 --> 09:22.280
Can I see you for the fifth time?

09:23.240 --> 09:25.160
Even if you don't change your mind,

09:25.800 --> 09:28.920
I'm happy that I can see you again.

09:30.720 --> 09:33.000
If you can live happily and freely,

09:33.520 --> 09:35.040
why bother seeing me?

09:36.560 --> 09:37.480
Take care of yourself.

09:57.960 --> 09:59.120
Mr. Wu.

09:59.720 --> 10:00.960
Physician, please.

10:02.880 --> 10:03.840
Wait a minute.

10:07.640 --> 10:08.840
Grandfather.

10:10.520 --> 10:13.480
This is… This is the imperial
physician sent by Yan Tang.

10:14.520 --> 10:15.960
Imperial physician?

10:18.040 --> 10:21.920
Can you turn around
and let me take a look?

10:40.480 --> 10:41.600
Physician Li!

10:43.680 --> 10:44.520
Mr. Wu.

10:45.040 --> 10:47.600
Mr. Song is meeting Physician Li
at Guanghe Restaurant.

10:47.680 --> 10:50.080
I was asked to take Physician Li over.

10:54.200 --> 10:55.360
In that case,

10:56.400 --> 10:59.240
it's inconvenient
to force the physician to stay.

11:07.520 --> 11:10.080
You were willing to see this physician.

11:11.280 --> 11:12.680
This physician…

11:13.640 --> 11:15.240
I'm afraid her surname is Dou.

11:17.240 --> 11:18.680
Now that you've seen her,

11:19.800 --> 11:21.480
have a good rest.

11:24.360 --> 11:25.400
Grandfather.

11:27.480 --> 11:29.880
I was wrong.

11:32.680 --> 11:34.040
Since I became mature,

11:35.280 --> 11:37.520
you arranged everything for me.

11:38.960 --> 11:42.040
The books that I read…
The friends that I made…

11:43.160 --> 11:44.720
The teachers that I learned from…

11:46.600 --> 11:47.920
The government office where I should work…

11:48.920 --> 11:51.960
You even arranged my breakfast.

11:53.680 --> 11:56.960
Sometimes I really envy Dou Zhao

11:59.320 --> 12:00.720
and Yan Tang.

12:02.160 --> 12:03.960
They're unrestrained.

12:17.960 --> 12:19.000
Grandfather.

12:19.560 --> 12:23.480
I know the imperial court
is dangerous and unpredictable.

12:24.080 --> 12:27.160
You're maintaining
the family status alone.

12:30.640 --> 12:35.480
I should work hard and strive to
overcome difficulties with you.

12:52.800 --> 12:54.800
It's Dou Shi Shu's order.

12:55.320 --> 12:57.600
The Duke of Ding's Army at Futing
was disarmed.

12:58.120 --> 12:59.720
The Duke of Ding is accused of
having evil intentions,

12:59.800 --> 13:01.680
so all soldiers are deported
to their hometowns.

13:03.640 --> 13:05.800
Young Lady Zhao was here to hold you back.

13:06.920 --> 13:08.800
She even caught Physician Li.

13:22.520 --> 13:24.320
The court took action against
the Duke of Ding's Army.

13:25.360 --> 13:26.240
This is Uncle Shi Shu's doing.

13:27.000 --> 13:28.680
I took a risk to save Song Mo.

13:28.760 --> 13:31.520
Everything that I did
had removed his hostility.

13:32.640 --> 13:34.160
But it's all in vain now.

13:39.480 --> 13:42.240
Mr. Song.
Young Lady Zhao's carriage is arriving.

13:44.680 --> 13:45.560
All right.

13:46.920 --> 13:49.560
Go greet her for me.

13:50.160 --> 13:51.000
Yes.

13:59.400 --> 14:01.080
My lady, something's wrong.

14:12.440 --> 14:15.200
Young Lady Zhao, you diverted
our attention to do something else.

14:15.280 --> 14:17.000
That's a brilliant trick.

14:17.520 --> 14:18.560
I'm asking questions
on behalf of Mr. Song.

14:19.320 --> 14:20.520
Young Lady Zhao.

14:21.120 --> 14:22.440
What's your explanation?

14:28.400 --> 14:29.600
WINE LODGE

14:39.480 --> 14:40.680
I have nothing to explain.

14:55.080 --> 14:57.720
Mr. Song said the covenant was broken.

14:57.800 --> 15:00.080
Chen Qu Shui will not be returned to you.

15:00.160 --> 15:01.280
When we meet again,

15:02.560 --> 15:03.880
we'll be enemies.

15:15.760 --> 15:17.080
My lady, why didn't you explain?

15:17.720 --> 15:19.120
This is Fifth Master's doing.

15:19.200 --> 15:20.600
It has nothing to do with you.

15:23.440 --> 15:24.680
If he trusts me,

15:25.440 --> 15:26.720
I don't have to explain.

15:28.040 --> 15:29.240
But if he doesn't trust me,

15:30.160 --> 15:31.400
any explanation is useless.

15:32.320 --> 15:33.440
It's better not to say anything.

15:34.480 --> 15:35.560
Don't blame yourself, my lady.

15:36.160 --> 15:38.440
We can't disobey the edict.

15:42.240 --> 15:44.080
Mr. Song, are we going to let it go?

15:45.280 --> 15:48.080
The truth is still unknown.

15:48.880 --> 15:51.320
If she had planned to trick me
by doing me a favor first,

15:52.120 --> 15:54.080
she wouldn't have
straightened De Zhen out.

15:56.360 --> 15:57.520
We'll see how it goes.

15:59.040 --> 16:02.120
You took all precautions,
but it wasn't enough.

16:02.920 --> 16:05.800
Young Lady Zhao is inscrutable
while Mr. Song is soft-hearted.

16:05.880 --> 16:09.720
It'll be safe if you marry her
and keep her at home.

16:10.240 --> 16:11.080
I guess you're looking for fun.

16:11.160 --> 16:12.440
-You want to get smacked.
-I…

16:15.640 --> 16:17.040
I found you!

16:19.520 --> 16:21.920
The Jiying Guards found some clues.

16:31.920 --> 16:35.120
As expected. Someone was missing.

16:39.080 --> 16:41.320
You owe me 300 taels
yet you dare to play tricks again.

16:42.000 --> 16:44.280
What a bold gambler you are!

16:46.320 --> 16:47.360
I told you.

16:47.880 --> 16:50.080
Someone will definitely pay my debt.

16:50.160 --> 16:51.920
Well, you treat me like a fool.

16:53.640 --> 16:55.960
He'll be worthless
if you beat him to death.

16:58.720 --> 17:00.560
Mr. Mei has something to ask him.

17:01.080 --> 17:02.880
Mister, please make some room.

17:05.000 --> 17:07.000
Here comes the person to pay my debt.

17:10.680 --> 17:12.400
You were once the squad leader
of the Jiying Guards.

17:12.480 --> 17:14.520
Based on your previous position,

17:14.599 --> 17:16.240
your annual salary
is no more than 10 taels.

17:16.760 --> 17:19.160
But in just a few days,
you owed 300 taels.

17:19.240 --> 17:21.359
No wonder you were dismissed.

17:22.040 --> 17:24.359
Compared with what you want to know,

17:24.880 --> 17:27.359
300 taels is probably
not worth mentioning.

17:31.480 --> 17:33.800
If you lie while gambling,
your hands will be cut off.

17:34.640 --> 17:36.240
If you lie to me,

17:37.000 --> 17:38.320
your life will be gone!

17:38.400 --> 17:39.400
That's for sure.

17:43.600 --> 17:45.200
You must have checked
my background, right?

17:45.840 --> 17:47.320
Based on the records of
the Criminal Investigation Service,

17:47.400 --> 17:50.160
eight Jiying Guards were responsible
for the journey to the south.

17:50.680 --> 17:52.480
I checked the directions
along the waterway.

17:52.560 --> 17:54.720
I originally wanted to learn
the identities of these eight.

17:55.680 --> 17:57.520
But all the clues showed that

17:58.120 --> 17:59.640
there were nine people.

18:02.400 --> 18:03.440
And you…

18:04.040 --> 18:06.640
You're the ninth person.

18:07.840 --> 18:09.600
ZHAOWEN BOOKSTORE

18:09.680 --> 18:10.720
An Su?

18:11.360 --> 18:12.680
Why did you come here?

18:13.520 --> 18:14.360
DOU ZHAO, READ IMMEDIATELY

18:14.440 --> 18:15.760
Mr. Ji wrote a letter from Futing.

18:16.440 --> 18:18.320
Someone from the Maritime Trade Office
seized my ships.

18:18.400 --> 18:19.760
They even put my family in jail!

18:19.840 --> 18:21.360
The Fifth Master brought
a message to the farm.

18:22.120 --> 18:24.440
He told you to cut off
your relationship with my family

18:24.520 --> 18:26.160
and business dealings.

18:30.240 --> 18:32.840
But there were only eight bodies
of the Jiying Guards on the ship.

18:32.920 --> 18:36.160
I remember the looks of the eight
Jiying Guards on the ship.

18:43.600 --> 18:45.120
Only you, Chen Jia.

18:45.800 --> 18:47.000
You were not on the ship.

18:49.320 --> 18:51.640
Indeed, you're like people say.

18:52.320 --> 18:53.720
You remember everything you have seen.

18:53.800 --> 18:55.720
Stop the nonsense! Explain it!

18:57.440 --> 18:59.560
Chen Zu Xun, the battalion leader
who was responsible for escorting

18:59.640 --> 19:00.640
the Duke of Ding was my adoptive father.

19:01.240 --> 19:03.280
My name was not on the list.

19:03.800 --> 19:04.960
He wanted me to atone for
my crimes and obtained a credit,

19:05.040 --> 19:06.320
so he brought me along.

19:11.120 --> 19:13.080
That night, when we
reached the Cangzhou River,

19:13.160 --> 19:15.120
we docked for a break.

19:15.200 --> 19:17.400
But a group of people
boarded the ship to visit.

19:24.960 --> 19:26.400
I was getting some air at the stern.

19:26.920 --> 19:28.680
Suddenly I heard the sound
of killing coming from the cabin.

19:30.240 --> 19:32.040
They used the bandit knife of Dongyu.

19:32.120 --> 19:34.320
But they were not using
Dongyu's sword technique.

19:34.840 --> 19:36.200
They were excellent.

19:36.280 --> 19:37.960
Even the Jiying Guards
couldn't compete with them.

19:42.120 --> 19:43.960
My adoptive father
was also killed by them.

19:47.200 --> 19:48.800
I was no match for them.

19:50.000 --> 19:53.240
I escaped by jumping into the water.

19:56.840 --> 19:58.280
Who are those people?

20:00.000 --> 20:01.680
If you keep asking,

20:03.680 --> 20:05.640
I'm afraid 1,000 taels is not enough.

20:10.560 --> 20:12.000
You obviously don't know about them.

20:13.080 --> 20:15.440
Yet you dared to bargain.

20:16.120 --> 20:17.560
Ring finger or little finger?

20:19.600 --> 20:21.240
I'm a gambler, to begin with.

20:22.320 --> 20:24.640
I am treated indifferently. I have debts.

20:25.440 --> 20:27.480
My adoptive father, the only one
who treated me as a human being,

20:27.560 --> 20:28.840
died a violent death.

20:29.840 --> 20:31.800
It doesn't matter whether
it's my fingers or my life.

20:32.760 --> 20:34.560
Take whatever you want!

20:43.240 --> 20:45.480
Dogs salivate when they hear
the sound of a bowl being knocked.

20:46.400 --> 20:49.040
Gamblers want to play a game when
they hear the sound of dice rolling.

20:49.120 --> 20:51.640
You can find a future
with the skills you have.

20:51.720 --> 20:53.800
That's why your adoptive father
refused to give up on you.

20:53.880 --> 20:56.520
But he was blind!

20:57.240 --> 20:58.680
You have no right to mention
my adoptive father!

21:01.880 --> 21:03.320
The grace of parenting
is greater than ever.

21:04.000 --> 21:07.200
Those who killed him killed my uncle too.

21:07.720 --> 21:09.640
You don't want to take revenge
to repay his kindness.

21:09.720 --> 21:11.640
You want to dream and
get drunk at the gambling table,

21:11.720 --> 21:13.280
and live without any purpose?

21:18.360 --> 21:20.040
I've seen through it.

21:22.840 --> 21:24.360
Be it a squad leader

21:25.080 --> 21:26.560
or a battalion leader,

21:27.800 --> 21:30.800
the Jiying Guards are nothing
but lackeys ordered around by others.

21:31.680 --> 21:34.360
They're just some ants that
can be crushed to death casually.

21:36.080 --> 21:37.080
This revenge…

21:38.560 --> 21:40.400
Even if I risk my life,
I can't take revenge!

21:42.280 --> 21:43.720
I don't know who those people were.

21:44.760 --> 21:46.440
But the leader was wearing
a crimson official uniform.

21:46.520 --> 21:48.440
He must be someone of fifth rank or below.

21:48.520 --> 21:51.200
My adoptive father allowed him to pass
and greeted him as "sir".

21:52.400 --> 21:53.880
He must be a senior official
in the imperial court.

21:53.960 --> 21:56.440
Who ordered the Jiying Guards
to torture him like that?

21:56.520 --> 21:57.880
They were under a secret order.

21:57.960 --> 21:59.560
Before arriving in the capital,
the Duke of Ding

21:59.640 --> 22:00.960
must admit to the crime
of having autocratic military power.

22:01.040 --> 22:02.240
Whose secret order?

22:05.440 --> 22:06.640
My adoptive father never revealed.

22:13.800 --> 22:14.840
Mr. Song!

22:16.480 --> 22:18.400
I never dared to think about this before.

22:19.920 --> 22:20.920
But after meeting you

22:21.520 --> 22:23.120
and listening to what you said,

22:24.600 --> 22:27.280
I do not want to waste my life anymore.

22:28.280 --> 22:31.040
I want revenge.

22:32.400 --> 22:34.680
I want my life to be clear.

22:35.280 --> 22:36.400
Mr. Song, please fulfill my wish!

22:36.480 --> 22:38.440
I'm willing to pay for it with my life!

22:38.520 --> 22:40.880
How can we trust the words
of a gambler who cheats?

22:50.080 --> 22:51.160
Tell the Count of Yunyang to find ways

22:51.800 --> 22:53.760
to send him back to
the Criminal Investigation Service.

22:54.560 --> 22:56.480
-Yes.
-You'll be mine from now on.

22:58.040 --> 22:59.520
The finger…

22:59.600 --> 23:03.160
Keep it so that you can
hold the sword to fight for me.

23:05.640 --> 23:07.560
MIAO SHIP SEIZED BY FUTING TRADE OFFICE
FUTING TURMOIL, MIAO FAMILY HEAD JAILED

23:11.160 --> 23:12.520
Zhao, don't be anxious.

23:12.600 --> 23:14.040
People from the Maritime Trade Office
have always been like this.

23:14.120 --> 23:16.000
Their bite is worse than their bark.

23:16.080 --> 23:17.320
They just want to get more benefits.

23:17.400 --> 23:19.560
I'll go to Futing
to deal with it right away.

23:19.640 --> 23:22.440
After all, this is related to
your principal and profit sharing.

23:23.920 --> 23:24.760
I'll go with you.

23:25.480 --> 23:26.600
What about Mr. Chen?

23:27.920 --> 23:31.360
Based on Song Mo's personality,
he won't hurt Mr. Chen easily.

23:31.440 --> 23:34.080
No. The Fifth Master
just sent his message.

23:34.160 --> 23:36.760
If the Maritime Trade Office
is asking for benefits,

23:37.440 --> 23:38.680
Uncle Shi Shu wouldn't know about this.

23:39.480 --> 23:40.640
He knows about this

23:41.160 --> 23:42.880
because the imperial court
is involved in this.

23:43.840 --> 23:45.360
I must go.

23:45.440 --> 23:46.360
The natural disaster
in Futing is not over yet

23:46.440 --> 23:47.840
and the soldiers are angry about it.

23:48.360 --> 23:49.520
Someone from the
Directorate of Ceremonial is there too.

23:50.200 --> 23:51.720
It must be an extremely dangerous mess.

23:52.320 --> 23:53.880
We can't let Zhao take risks then.

23:53.960 --> 23:57.240
No matter what happens,
I will definitely return the principal.

23:59.040 --> 24:00.320
What nonsense did you say?

24:01.240 --> 24:02.840
What I care about is not the money.

24:03.440 --> 24:05.560
It's the business we're doing.

24:05.640 --> 24:07.720
We can't let someone set up our business.

24:08.680 --> 24:12.040
If I go, maybe I can plan for a change.

24:13.280 --> 24:15.160
DUKE OF YING'S RESIDENCE

24:19.800 --> 24:20.840
Yan Tang!

24:26.360 --> 24:27.240
Mother.

24:29.080 --> 24:29.920
Why did you come out?

24:30.000 --> 24:33.880
General Yan said you're going to Futing
to retrieve Jiang's belongings.

24:35.200 --> 24:38.400
You can fool your father with this,
but not me.

24:39.600 --> 24:42.080
Did you find some clues
about your uncle's incident?

24:46.440 --> 24:48.360
Someone with a higher authority
is involved in this.

24:48.440 --> 24:49.800
I must go immediately.

24:50.320 --> 24:53.760
If it's too late,
I'm afraid all the clues will be lost.

24:54.920 --> 24:56.520
You're just like me.

24:57.400 --> 25:00.360
Once you make up your mind,
no one can stop you.

25:01.880 --> 25:04.640
The emperor told Wang Yuan
to take charge of this matter.

25:05.240 --> 25:09.200
When you're there, no matter what you get,
never go against Eunuch Wang.

25:10.560 --> 25:13.200
General Yan. Please.

25:14.000 --> 25:15.200
Rest assured, Mrs. Song.

25:15.280 --> 25:16.240
Mother.

25:17.480 --> 25:18.560
Don't worry.

25:19.280 --> 25:20.880
Your safety comes first.

25:21.720 --> 25:23.000
Don't force it.

25:26.240 --> 25:28.280
I've lost my elder brother.

25:29.880 --> 25:31.680
I can't afford to lose you.

25:38.000 --> 25:40.400
Come on, put it on.

25:44.240 --> 25:47.400
Fortunately, I mended this cloak.

26:02.280 --> 26:03.120
Go.

26:12.640 --> 26:13.480
Mother.

26:14.120 --> 26:14.960
Wait for my return.

26:42.400 --> 26:44.120
What's wrong with Zhao?

26:44.200 --> 26:46.600
She's been like this
since she met Mr. Song.

26:46.680 --> 26:50.320
She's probably worried
because Mr. Chen didn't return.

26:52.640 --> 26:56.320
Zhao. Eat something.
You've not eaten anything for a day.

26:57.440 --> 26:59.480
I'm not hungry. You should eat.

27:04.880 --> 27:08.720
I wonder how's the farm now.
Will something happen?

27:18.400 --> 27:20.480
Young Lady Zhao's pulse
sounds healthy and strong.

27:20.560 --> 27:22.520
She seems fine.

27:22.600 --> 27:23.880
How could she be fine?

27:23.960 --> 27:26.200
Shou Gu has blisters all over her body
and is extremely itchy.

27:26.280 --> 27:27.880
I think you have poor skills.

27:29.680 --> 27:31.800
You should check again.

27:34.840 --> 27:35.880
Wait a minute!

27:36.720 --> 27:38.240
Her pulse goes up and down.

27:38.320 --> 27:39.680
This… This is weird!

27:39.760 --> 27:41.000
This is weird!

27:41.080 --> 27:42.400
By the way, Young Lady Zhao,

27:42.480 --> 27:45.360
about your blisters,
can you let me take a look?

27:45.440 --> 27:46.840
What? Take a look my foot!

27:46.920 --> 27:48.600
She's a lady!

27:48.680 --> 27:50.400
You're such a pervert! Leave!

27:50.480 --> 27:51.880
-Go prescribe the medicine!
-That's not it…

27:51.960 --> 27:52.800
Slow down…

27:53.320 --> 27:54.240
Grandmother.

27:54.320 --> 27:56.120
How's Shou Gu? Let me take a look.

27:56.800 --> 27:59.240
Don't look. Shou Gu has chicken pox.

27:59.320 --> 28:01.120
We'll be worried
if you're infected with it.

28:01.200 --> 28:03.600
Besides, the physician
has prescribed medicine.

28:03.680 --> 28:05.040
She will recover in two weeks.

28:05.120 --> 28:06.960
What's the use of having medicine only?

28:07.040 --> 28:09.480
It's painful to have chicken pox.

28:09.560 --> 28:11.240
Let me take a look.

28:11.320 --> 28:12.440
-Grandmother!
-Slowly…

28:12.520 --> 28:14.280
Grandmother, don't come in!

28:14.360 --> 28:16.080
You're not fully recovered yet.

28:16.160 --> 28:19.720
If you're infected too,
I'll feel even more guilty.

28:20.520 --> 28:22.160
Look. I told you.

28:22.240 --> 28:23.600
I had chicken pox before.

28:23.680 --> 28:25.360
I'm the most suitable one
to take care of Shou Gu.

28:25.440 --> 28:28.000
Just go back and have a good rest.

28:28.080 --> 28:31.520
Don't worry. I'll give you
the chubby Shou Gu after a few days.

28:31.600 --> 28:33.480
-Are you sure you can handle it?
-Go. You should go too.

28:34.080 --> 28:35.400
Don't worry, I'm here.

28:38.040 --> 28:39.640
God, God of Wealth, Guan Yu,
please bless that

28:40.240 --> 28:42.200
Shou Gu and Su Su return safely.

28:44.920 --> 28:47.000
Mr. Shi Shu was appointed
as the assistant imperial censor

28:47.080 --> 28:48.880
while Mr. Wang was promoted
to Grand Secretariat.

28:48.960 --> 28:51.440
We should meet up frequently.

28:51.520 --> 28:54.640
Our lives will get better with Ms. Wang.

28:54.720 --> 28:58.760
We'll just have to wait for profits
from the money we keep with Ms. Wang

29:00.800 --> 29:01.640
Pong!

29:04.720 --> 29:06.000
Seventh Madam.

29:09.000 --> 29:10.280
Excuse me.

29:12.760 --> 29:15.000
Whose turn to draw the tile?

29:16.120 --> 29:17.280
-It seems to be yours.
-Seventh Madam.

29:17.800 --> 29:18.960
Someone at the city gate

29:19.040 --> 29:22.560
saw Young Lady Zhao and Ms. Miao
go out of the city and head south.

29:23.760 --> 29:25.240
I see. You may go now.

29:25.320 --> 29:26.240
Yes.

29:31.760 --> 29:33.800
She must be heading to Futing.

29:34.400 --> 29:38.440
The Miaos' merchant ships were detained
by the Maritime Trade Office in Futing.

29:39.360 --> 29:41.600
She's anxious
as her financial path is cut off.

29:41.680 --> 29:44.240
An unmarried girl secretly left her house.

29:44.320 --> 29:45.760
This is against the family rules.

29:46.520 --> 29:49.400
She's showing us her weakness.

29:49.480 --> 29:52.160
You can take the opportunity
to get her back and question her.

29:53.320 --> 29:56.800
No rush. If I capture her now…

29:56.880 --> 29:58.440
Well, she fails to escape.

29:58.520 --> 30:00.680
At most, she'll be punished to kneel
in the ancestral hall for a few days.

30:01.280 --> 30:03.280
Dou Shi Ying will feel distressed again.

30:04.160 --> 30:06.160
Isn't she a tough one?

30:07.440 --> 30:10.680
Futing is like a tiger's den now.

30:10.760 --> 30:12.800
Let's see how capable she is.

30:13.520 --> 30:16.320
FUTING

30:16.400 --> 30:18.480
-Here.
-Give me some food.

30:22.960 --> 30:23.960
Move!

30:29.560 --> 30:32.400
Please… Give me some food.

30:32.480 --> 30:35.200
You can exchange tea for rice…

30:35.280 --> 30:37.120
Eight dou of tea for one dou of rice.

30:37.640 --> 30:38.600
-Don't push!
-Here.

30:38.680 --> 30:40.000
-Step back!
-Don't snatch it…

30:40.080 --> 30:41.720
-Everyone will get it!
-You'll have it.

30:41.800 --> 30:43.000
-Slow down…
-Everyone will get it.

30:43.080 --> 30:44.160
-Everyone will get it.
-Don't rush. Everyone will get it.

30:44.240 --> 30:46.240
-Here.
-Don't push!

30:46.320 --> 30:47.160
Don't push!

30:47.240 --> 30:48.840
STRONG FOUNDATIONS ENSURE
NATIONAL STABILITY

30:55.600 --> 30:57.440
How did Futing become like this?

30:57.520 --> 30:59.480
They don't even have food.

31:00.320 --> 31:03.080
The maritime trade has been
prospering, so tea earns better.

31:03.600 --> 31:05.120
People have switched to tea plantations.

31:05.720 --> 31:08.120
When the Duke of Ding died,
the maritime trade stopped.

31:08.760 --> 31:11.560
So they can't sell the tea.

31:11.640 --> 31:12.880
That's right.

31:14.480 --> 31:15.760
Doesn't the government care?

31:16.360 --> 31:17.240
Who dares to meddle?

31:17.320 --> 31:19.200
Whoever does is a profiteer
like the Miao family.

31:19.800 --> 31:22.560
A few major tea houses funded the
Miao family when they built the ships.

31:22.640 --> 31:24.880
But the ships are seized now
and the money is wasted.

31:24.960 --> 31:26.480
The goods are still on the ship.

31:29.000 --> 31:30.840
It's my father's fault. He was greedy
and didn't listen to advice.

31:30.920 --> 31:32.680
He asked the commoners
to raise funds to build ships.

31:32.760 --> 31:34.080
In the end, many people were harmed.

31:35.880 --> 31:37.840
Uncle Miao didn't cheat on purpose.

31:37.920 --> 31:38.880
So he wasn't harming anyone.

31:38.960 --> 31:40.720
The suspension of the trading
and the seizing of the ships

31:40.800 --> 31:42.880
are the ones that
cut off people's livelihood.

31:44.400 --> 31:47.000
When we enter the city,
let's meet up with Ji Yong first.

31:47.680 --> 31:48.800
The state affairs of Futing

31:49.400 --> 31:50.920
and the intention of
the Maritime Trade Office,

31:51.000 --> 31:52.120
he must know better than us.

31:53.760 --> 31:57.040
Su Lan, buy some more rations.
We've got a long way to go.

31:57.120 --> 31:57.960
Alright.

32:03.920 --> 32:04.800
Stop right there.

32:04.880 --> 32:06.160
Stop right there!

32:09.800 --> 32:11.360
It's not her. Go.

32:14.240 --> 32:15.080
Go.

32:20.560 --> 32:22.080
You're Ms. Miao, right?

32:22.720 --> 32:25.640
Mr. Ding Wei, the general manager of the
Maritime Trade Office invites you over.

32:26.360 --> 32:27.240
And you.

32:27.880 --> 32:29.400
You must be Dou Zhao, right?

32:29.480 --> 32:30.480
Take them away.

32:30.560 --> 32:31.800
TEA

32:38.520 --> 32:41.040
TEA

32:52.200 --> 32:53.480
Ji Yong.

33:01.320 --> 33:03.520
FUTING COUNTY OFFICE, GOVERNMENT YAMEN

33:10.920 --> 33:11.880
Loosen the ties.

33:15.960 --> 33:19.080
The Miao family secretly
communicated with the pirates.

33:19.160 --> 33:20.400
The evidence is conclusive.

33:26.360 --> 33:29.080
If you sign it, you're pleading guilty.

33:30.120 --> 33:33.760
If you don't sign it, there'll be
another crime under your name.

33:35.320 --> 33:36.360
No way.

33:36.440 --> 33:38.040
My father would never
collude with the enemy.

33:38.960 --> 33:40.920
The Miao family is engaged
in maritime trade.

33:41.000 --> 33:43.160
The pirates kill and rob at sea.

33:43.240 --> 33:44.560
They're hated.

33:44.640 --> 33:45.880
Why would the Miaos collude with them?

33:48.720 --> 33:50.440
When the maritime trade was banned,

33:50.520 --> 33:52.920
there were many unscrupulous people
who colluded with pirates.

33:53.000 --> 33:55.760
He must have benefitted from the pirates,

33:55.840 --> 33:58.440
that was why he dared to collude
with them to kill someone.

33:59.760 --> 34:01.040
You're suspecting that the Miao family

34:01.120 --> 34:02.360
colluded with the pirates
to kill the Duke of Ding.

34:03.880 --> 34:05.840
This is the heinous crime of murdering
the trusted adviser to the nation.

34:05.920 --> 34:07.440
How can you simply decide the case?

34:08.199 --> 34:11.320
Besides, Eunuch Wang Yuan
is also here in Futing.

34:11.840 --> 34:14.320
How are you going to explain
if you make a mistake in the sentence?

34:16.000 --> 34:17.040
You're presumptuous!

34:17.560 --> 34:19.520
You know it's a serious crime
and you're still being loud.

34:20.120 --> 34:21.639
Present the evidence!

34:24.159 --> 34:25.960
Take a good look.

34:26.040 --> 34:28.920
These knives from the pirates
were found on your ship.

34:29.440 --> 34:33.000
It's the same as the knife
that killed the Duke of Ding.

34:33.080 --> 34:36.080
This is irrefutable evidence that
you committed murder.

34:36.719 --> 34:37.719
This is impossible.

34:38.480 --> 34:40.400
I filled in the ship's account book.

34:40.480 --> 34:43.120
We were sending tea leaves, fruits,
silk, and porcelain for this trip.

34:43.199 --> 34:44.239
There were no weapons.

34:44.320 --> 34:46.600
Xue Ping, the escort,
Li Gui, who did the inventory count,

34:46.679 --> 34:48.880
and Officer Liu of the Maritime Trade
Office who filed for preliminary review

34:48.960 --> 34:50.159
can testify to this.

34:50.679 --> 34:51.960
Mr. Ding.

34:52.520 --> 34:53.679
Where are those witnesses?

34:53.760 --> 34:54.960
-That's right!
-Right!

34:55.040 --> 34:56.239
That's right!

34:56.320 --> 34:57.280
Where are the witnesses?

34:57.360 --> 34:58.800
That's right! Present them!

34:58.880 --> 35:00.240
Don't accuse good people!

35:00.320 --> 35:01.560
Be quiet!

35:01.640 --> 35:04.480
Who are you to teach me
how to handle the case?

35:05.200 --> 35:06.600
You want witnesses, right?

35:07.120 --> 35:08.920
Aren't you witnesses too?

35:09.000 --> 35:11.320
Guards! Send them to the prison!

35:14.280 --> 35:15.880
You can interrogate me.
But do not drag her into this.

35:16.480 --> 35:17.960
She is Dou Zhao, the granddaughter
of the Cui family from Ji'an,

35:18.040 --> 35:19.880
the eldest daughter of the Dou's
Residence in the west of the capital.

35:19.960 --> 35:20.840
How dare you hurt her!

35:20.920 --> 35:22.280
The Miao family's affairs
are our family affairs too.

35:23.400 --> 35:26.040
I was ordered by my family to
clear the misunderstanding first.

35:26.560 --> 35:27.800
My family will arrive soon.

35:28.400 --> 35:30.160
Do you still want to frame us?

35:31.480 --> 35:33.400
Relatives of the minister
with a higher position…

35:33.480 --> 35:36.680
Maybe I can find out
your cliques and ulterior motives.

35:36.760 --> 35:37.960
I'll gain more credit then.

35:38.040 --> 35:39.080
Take them away!

35:43.920 --> 35:46.240
PRISON

35:56.000 --> 35:56.920
Stop.

36:01.840 --> 36:07.200
Why didn't you interrogate me in the hall,
in front of the crowd?

36:07.880 --> 36:10.520
Do you know that abuse of power

36:11.040 --> 36:13.440
and confessions extorted by torture
are serious crimes?

36:14.040 --> 36:16.480
You're a smart person.

36:17.000 --> 36:20.320
I just want a documented confession.

36:20.400 --> 36:23.480
If you testify against the Miaos,

36:24.000 --> 36:25.600
I'll release you immediately.

36:26.160 --> 36:27.880
The Miao family didn't do it.

36:28.400 --> 36:30.280
Why should I testify against them?

36:32.240 --> 36:36.600
Then don't blame me
and say I didn't give you a chance.

36:58.480 --> 37:01.360
Well, I have interrogated Miao An Su.

37:01.440 --> 37:04.080
I pulled all her ten fingers.

37:04.800 --> 37:05.960
Take a good look.

37:06.600 --> 37:08.160
She has confessed.

37:09.640 --> 37:11.480
Sisterly love?

37:12.080 --> 37:14.280
If you don't testify against her,

37:14.360 --> 37:17.360
you'll be convicted, Ms. Dou.

37:20.160 --> 37:21.240
What are you laughing at?

37:21.840 --> 37:23.520
I laugh at you for being foolish.

37:24.400 --> 37:27.440
You didn't check her background
before slandering her.

37:27.520 --> 37:31.600
Even if someone
in this world would betray me,

37:32.360 --> 37:35.920
this person would never be Miao An Su.

37:37.680 --> 37:39.080
You have no witness.

37:39.160 --> 37:42.240
The case cannot be closed
if there's no witness.

37:43.240 --> 37:46.480
So you just want to find a scapegoat.

37:49.040 --> 37:50.280
Great.

37:50.920 --> 37:54.880
Looks like if I don't punish you heavily,
you will not admit it, right?

37:54.960 --> 37:56.720
Let's see if you dare to do it!

38:05.000 --> 38:06.200
If he doesn't dare to do it,

38:06.840 --> 38:07.880
I'll dare to do it.

38:09.160 --> 38:10.160
Song Mo?

38:10.960 --> 38:12.320
Mr. Song.

38:12.400 --> 38:13.480
Young Lady Zhao.

38:14.400 --> 38:15.360
We meet again.

38:19.840 --> 38:21.720
Mr. Ding, your finger-pinch punishment

38:21.800 --> 38:24.000
is like children playing house.

38:24.520 --> 38:25.760
What can you get from her?

38:30.680 --> 38:34.120
I've long heard about how good you are
at detecting lies during torture.

38:34.200 --> 38:35.800
No one in the world can compare to you.

38:36.400 --> 38:37.960
So Mr. Song,

38:40.120 --> 38:41.880
what kind of punishment should we use?

39:13.120 --> 39:15.960
When the flesh wound touches
the liquid from the feces,

39:16.840 --> 39:18.920
that will tear her apart.

39:40.120 --> 39:43.240
Song Mo has no military position now.
Why do you want to do him a favor?

39:43.320 --> 39:45.000
Indeed, he lost his military position.

39:45.080 --> 39:47.000
But he is the son of the Duke of Ying.

39:47.080 --> 39:50.440
I have owed him favors
since the day he was born.

39:50.960 --> 39:52.120
That's right.

39:52.200 --> 39:53.400
He is at odds with the Dou family.

39:53.480 --> 39:57.320
Wouldn't it be better
for him to finalize this case?

39:57.840 --> 39:58.680
You're right.

39:59.520 --> 40:02.680
My uncle's blood feud and your deception…

40:03.200 --> 40:04.320
Today,

40:05.200 --> 40:06.840
let's clear this up.

40:06.920 --> 40:09.200
I have a business partnership
with the Miao family.

40:09.880 --> 40:10.960
I earn a lot of money.

40:11.040 --> 40:13.560
That's because the Duke of Ding
suppressed the pirates at sea.

40:13.640 --> 40:15.320
What good would it do us to harm him?

40:18.880 --> 40:20.800
Of course, that's your reason.

40:21.400 --> 40:23.480
But as far as your uncle,
Dou Shi Shu, is concerned,

40:24.080 --> 40:26.400
he made no achievements
though he is ambitious.

40:26.480 --> 40:30.040
Killing my uncle
can cause chaos in the imperial court.

40:30.120 --> 40:32.360
He may rise to great heights.

40:33.600 --> 40:34.640
Power

40:35.520 --> 40:36.480
is more profitable.

40:36.560 --> 40:37.840
I told you before.

40:38.560 --> 40:40.200
Do not lump my fifth uncle
and me together!

40:43.200 --> 40:46.400
You lied to gain my trust,
informed your uncle of the news,

40:46.480 --> 40:48.600
and ordered the Duke of Ding's Army
to be disarmed and repatriated.

40:48.680 --> 40:50.320
Shouldn't I doubt you?

40:59.840 --> 41:02.920
Mr. Song has been fighting on
the battlefield since he was a child.

41:03.000 --> 41:05.520
He is indeed cold-hearted.

41:06.440 --> 41:08.120
She's such a charming woman.

41:08.200 --> 41:10.040
Yet he's ruthless to her.

41:14.200 --> 41:15.480
It's the medicinal powder used
in the military to treat bruises.

41:15.560 --> 41:16.840
It can cure your hand injury.

41:21.080 --> 41:22.120
You should scream, you know.

41:29.280 --> 41:31.680
Be serious. They're listening.

41:32.480 --> 41:34.000
-Scold me.
-Scold you?

41:34.080 --> 41:35.440
Yes, scold me.

41:37.920 --> 41:39.640
Is your zodiac sign the snake?

41:39.720 --> 41:41.200
You sure know how to "bite" someone.

41:41.280 --> 41:42.800
It was my fifth uncle
who was evil and confused you.

41:42.880 --> 41:44.960
Go interrogate him if you have the guts.

41:45.040 --> 41:46.600
Why bully me?

41:48.120 --> 41:50.320
You knew he was covering this up, right?

41:51.040 --> 41:53.680
-Yes. But do you have evidence?
-Take me to the ship.

41:53.760 --> 41:55.120
I'll find the evidence for you.

42:10.240 --> 42:11.520
It's so sick.

42:11.600 --> 42:13.960
I like it.

42:16.080 --> 42:17.280
There is one more thing.

42:17.800 --> 42:20.160
Sixteen years ago, the maritime trade
was not established yet.

42:20.240 --> 42:22.560
Futing had nine losses
out of ten in business.

42:22.640 --> 42:24.920
You were far away from Zhengding
and were still young.

42:25.520 --> 42:27.920
Why bet huge sums of money on Futing?

42:28.640 --> 42:29.680
If not premeditated,

42:31.120 --> 42:34.200
how did you know that
my uncle would eliminate pirates,

42:34.840 --> 42:36.480
thereby making huge profits?

42:36.560 --> 42:38.040
It was Mr. Chen's advice.

42:38.640 --> 42:40.040
He said the Duke of Ding was brave

42:40.120 --> 42:41.120
and able to quell the trouble.

42:43.840 --> 42:45.800
Miao An Su defended you.

42:45.880 --> 42:47.480
She said that at the start of the year,

42:47.560 --> 42:50.040
you had said that maritime trade
had reached its peak,

42:50.120 --> 42:52.400
and that it was time to pull out
of the business in Futing.

42:52.480 --> 42:53.680
It's as if

42:54.400 --> 42:56.840
you predicted my uncle's death.

42:57.680 --> 42:58.880
I can see that

42:58.960 --> 43:01.280
the things you hide in your heart
are related to me.

43:02.040 --> 43:03.800
Why won't you tell me?

43:06.320 --> 43:07.440
Say it!

43:25.800 --> 43:28.960
The emperor is ruthless and unjust.
He repaid kindness with hatred.

43:29.040 --> 43:31.640
A loyal minister and
a good general died in vain.

43:31.720 --> 43:33.560
That treacherous official,

43:34.600 --> 43:36.400
why can't it be me, Song Mo?

